        "timestamp": "2020-04-21 15:48:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\nHi,\n\nI have just pushed the last fixes and modifications and removed all the noise in order to make this change focused on adding `Try`. The remaining code will be pushed with another change once this one is validated.\n\nKeep in mind that the goal here is to replace `Either` by a data-structure that is easier to reason about and which provides the same semantic than exception handling.\n\nThank you in advance for your help,\n\nFrancis.",
        "patchset_number": 11
      },
